{"tid":2085283,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"帶無識寫app既人想創業...？","createTime":"2020-06-29T20:36:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T07:13:57.000Z","uid":210115,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2627019dc02d8cf4bd6c63675ebc74b8efe3361a","tid":2085283,"uid":210115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T20:36:25.000Z","msg":"香港地少人多，難以向上爬就係人都知<br />\n但係有無諗過識寫app既你其實喺依家呢知世代係好有機會？<br />\n<br />\n你只需要一個好既idea加上你既技能<br />\n就有機會逆轉你日日需要番工，拎份底薪呢個情況<br />\n當然，初期呢件事一定係大家親力親為<br />\n<br />\n但係我相信機會係留俾準備好既人💪🏻<br />\n<br />\n先自我介紹：<br />\n3字出頭，I大畢業，完全無business底，但近年邊做邊學<br />\n發覺就算有想法都無力做出黎（唔識寫app/program ,無錢請人做），但眼見現時商機處處，唔忍心再錯失機會<br />\n<br />\n現正邀請有心創業，想試下打工以外既選擇，歡迎認識下，出黎飲杯coffee傾傾<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係要sell你俾錢，純粹想搵同好一齊創業<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既手足麻煩留個tg傾傾"},{"pid":"1e08e3ffa3b30ad5903d237e720c81b5bcb3c60c","tid":2085283,"uid":124400,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T20:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mKXYHAm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmKXYHAm.png&h=7fae4795&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a15b2dd3c73e6fc08b989e328dca668b207bf217","tid":2085283,"uid":210115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e08e3ffa3b30ad5903d237e720c81b5bcb3c60c","tid":2085283,"uid":124400,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T20:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mKXYHAm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmKXYHAm.png&h=7fae4795&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T21:17:31.000Z","msg":"Um...似乎會寫app既人唔歡迎人地揸住idea黎傾啵..."},{"pid":"0878dfb8638dbb7f7c2aa8bd2c20d7b9165b0c3b","tid":2085283,"uid":124400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a15b2dd3c73e6fc08b989e328dca668b207bf217","tid":2085283,"uid":210115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e08e3ffa3b30ad5903d237e720c81b5bcb3c60c","tid":2085283,"uid":124400,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"r